<span id="freeTextContainer3787631288062686992">Drawn from original sources, <i>Old Path White Clouds</i> is the beautiful classic recounting of the life and teachings of Gautama Buddha over the course of eighty years. It is retold alternately through the eyes of Svasti, the buffalo boy who provided kusa grass for the Buddha&apos;s enlightenment cushion, and the Buddha himself.<br/></span>
