              <span id="reviewTextContainer2281296921" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7378525295660568041">Simple yet so profound. <br/>This books gives all the basic teachings of the Buddha 🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼</span>

          </span>
        </div>


