<div id="review_2374195985" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2374195985" />
    <a title="Đạt Phạm Quốc" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/57195312-t-ph-m-qu-c"><img alt="Đạt Phạm Quốc" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1467088654p2/57195312.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2374195985?book_show_action=true">Dec 21, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Đạt Phạm Quốc" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Đạt Phạm Quốc" href="/user/show/57195312-t-ph-m-qu-c">Đạt Phạm Quốc</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2374195985" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6583487175783850681">Reading this book is just like relaxing and meditating. We could see the Buddha so closely as if he and the his students are just sitting right next to us. The book not only provides the stories/history of the life of the Buddha, but also provides the basic concepts/ideas in Buddhism, which are very entry-level, very easy to read and understand. Just like we are studying Buddhism through reading this novel.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

