      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/255251-old-path-white-clouds-walking-in-the-footsteps-of-the-buddha">Quotes from Old Path White Cl...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
